@startuml
!theme aws-orange
actor Employee
participant "VTS System" as VTS
database DB
participant "Email Service" as Email
actor Manager

== Access VTS ==

Employee -> VTS : Open VTS via portal

alt Authentication failed
    VTS --> Employee : Show authentication error
else Authenticated
    VTS -> DB : Fetch requests & balances
    DB --> VTS : Return data
    VTS --> Employee : Display dashboard
end


== Select Request ==

Employee -> VTS : Select approved request to cancel
VTS --> Employee : Display request details


== Cancel Request ==

alt Request in future
    VTS --> Employee : Ask for cancellation confirmation

    alt Employee confirms
        VTS -> DB : Update request (Canceled)
        VTS -> DB : Restore vacation balance
        VTS -> Email : Notify manager
        Email -> Manager : Send cancellation email
    else Employee aborts
        VTS --> Employee : No changes made
    end

else Request in recent past (max 5 days)
    VTS --> Employee : Ask for confirmation + explanation

    alt Employee confirms with explanation
        Employee -> VTS : Submit explanation
        VTS -> DB : Update request (Canceled)
        VTS -> DB : Restore vacation balance
        VTS -> Email : Notify manager
        Email -> Manager : Send cancellation email
    else Employee aborts
        VTS --> Employee : No changes made
    end
end


== Return to Home ==

VTS -> DB : Refresh requests & balances
DB --> VTS : Updated data
VTS --> Employee : Display updated dashboard
@enduml